{"tid":539193,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"山陰深度遊 有問有答","createTime":"2018-01-24T10:47:44.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-23T15:32:39.000Z","uid":168548,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"a0d98098aa2019c5f61c7e7b18013424a45a88bb","tid":539193,"uid":168548,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-24T10:47:44.000Z","msg":"上年一家去左山陽山陰之旅,發覺冷門有冷門的玩發!今年再黎一個山陰深度遊,如果大家有興趣去山陰可以入黎一齊吹下水<br />\n<br />\n去山陰最方便係直飛米子,機票夠平,7月中都係2300全包!<br />\n<br />\n咁山陰有乜地方有乜正?和牛 溫泉 魚生,某程度計仲平過沖繩!<br />\n<br />\n現的地方有鳥取砂丘(必去)就好多人知,但蒜山高原及大山地區都係必到的<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/01/24/184702_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F01%2F24%2F184702_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=99d27178&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n大山區在米子揸車30分鐘就到,非常方便,其中一個叫 森之國的戶外營地我囝囝去完不停話要再去<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.sanin.com/daisen/morinokuni/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.sanin.com%2Fdaisen%2Fmorinokuni%2F&d=FwDw7Z2ps91hg4DRjL4wAGi1w7%2FDyS2Kz%2BsYtkalU0Y%3D&h=952156f1\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.sanin.com/daisen/morinokuni/</a><br />\n<br />\n食野方便有境港呢個日本第三大魚港<br />\n食蟹真係平到無朋友,一條鯛只要700yen,我無打少一個0<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/01/24/184712_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F01%2F24%2F184712_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=38ebf596&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"93b8e685688fbf19be97cdb495d6441e1cacc9c7","tid":539193,"uid":281,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-24T11:19:36.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"fb64119a0f66505b4e70842f7b964e0f486bc23d","tid":539193,"uid":129378,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"93b8e685688fbf19be97cdb495d6441e1cacc9c7","tid":539193,"uid":281,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-24T11:19:36.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-24T12:08:34.000Z","msg":"由鳥取開始：沙丘，浦富海岸，仁風閣，倉吉，三朝溫泉，米子，境港，大山。<br />\n島根：松江，出雲，石見銀山，秋芳洞。<br />\n山口唔熟<br />\n廣島：錦帶橋，嚴島，廣島市，尾道<br />\n岡山：倉Fu 美觀地區，岡山城後樂園，吉備津神社，備前地區，蒜山高原"},{"pid":"72b70e10b0fe4a9f1f0fc28774d6cdb32da869e2","tid":539193,"uid":26230,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-24T12:09:28.000Z","msg":"留名"},{"pid":"3d9bfc13072342f35a393369bbaf682281f77ca2","tid":539193,"uid":23951,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-24T12:11:03.000Z","msg":"有冇係大山滑雪？"},{"pid":"cadd2dbe95b9d867815d139020a241dc1505a02b","tid":539193,"uid":26230,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-24T12:11:54.000Z","msg":"巴打會去咩左地方？同埋去左幾多日？"},{"pid":"24edd24a15845c3cde57e5b825d7a062622e2256","tid":539193,"uid":281,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-24T12:26:49.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"8146addcd580ac0b2730d835ddf0369fa86be237","tid":539193,"uid":35372,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fb64119a0f66505b4e70842f7b964e0f486bc23d","tid":539193,"uid":129378,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"93b8e685688fbf19be97cdb495d6441e1cacc9c7","tid":539193,"uid":281,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-24T11:19:36.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-24T12:08:34.000Z","msg":"由鳥取開始：沙丘，浦富海岸，仁風閣，倉吉，三朝溫泉，米子，境港，大山。<br />\n島根：松江，出雲，石見銀山，秋芳洞。<br />\n山口唔熟<br />\n廣島：錦帶橋，嚴島，廣島市，尾道<br />\n岡山：倉Fu 美觀地區，岡山城後樂園，吉備津神社，備前地區，蒜山高原"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-24T12:32:26.000Z","msg":"山口:角島,元乃xx神社(呢兩個無車完全唔洗諗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ),下關,山口市<br />\n秋芳洞同秋吉台係大伏黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"94432a35b08ecf77170f00a6d2397fabe244f979","tid":539193,"uid":281,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-24T12:44:53.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"25c9b8b5fb9182ca64da3664b91e6e758422791f","tid":539193,"ui